        <iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d320.17429140243024!2d21.991295970040735!3d50.06017629754254!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x473cfb79d8d6a205%3A0xee90b09c846707d4!2sInneftech!5e0!3m2!1spl!2spl!4v1691534531933!5m2!1spl!2spl" width="600" height="450" style="border:0;" allowfullscreen="" loading="lazy" referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"></iframe>
    </div>
